{"id":3265,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">本文侧重于从宏观（社会、历史、经济）的视角，加以辨析。题录如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">一．样板戏里的表述</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">二．20世纪后半叶人类社会的两大收获</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">三．国有、集体所有，都不是公有制</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">四． 世界大同、共产主义，都是乌托邦</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">五．听从社会实践的检验</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">六。从心理学来看</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">一．样板戏里的表述</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.35pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">在《龙江颂》中</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.35pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">江水英</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">：</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">手捧宝书满心暖，一轮红曰照胸间。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">毫不利己破私念，专门利人公在先。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">有私念近在咫尺人隔远，立公字遥距天涯心相连。读宝书耳边如闻党召唤， </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">似战鼓催征人快马加鞭。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.35pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">这类表述虽不很多，但通过人物形象，对破私立公的表现，却也不少。此处不必列举。破私立公、大公无私、公而忘私、无私奉献、毫不利己专门利人、狠斗私字一闪念等，几十年来，成为主流媒体宣扬的伦理学的信条。现在到了该进行辨析、清算的时候了。文</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">[1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3],</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">从微观方面，已做过一些分析。本文侧重于从宏观（社会、历史、经济）的视角，加以辨析。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>二．20世纪后半叶人类社会的两大收获</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.35pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1. </FONT></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">两大收获</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.35pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">世纪前半叶发生过两次世界大战、一系列国家的革命，热战频繁。随后进入东西两大集团冷战对峙的时期。与此同时，社会主义阵营各国，先后开始实行改革。随着中国摆脱文革，走向改革开放、中美关系改善、苏联东欧一场巨变，到上世纪末，全世界结束冷战对峙，进入以和平、发展、合作为主体的新时代。这是人类社会，从野蛮逐步走向文明的一个重要转折。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">与此同时，实行市场经济的国家、地区，在不断的批判、改良中，克服危机，焕发活力，并引领世界经济的发展。社会主义阵营各国实行的计划经济，弊端频出，穷途末路，最终全部在改革中被市场经济所取而代之。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">这两大收获，互相联系，第二个更为深刻。市场经济、计划经济，熟优熟劣，全人类的社会实践，已经做出了最有说服了的结论。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2. </FONT></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">市场经济为何优越与计划经济</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">⑴资源的优化配置。计划经济的实质，是把整个社会组织成为一个单一的大工厂，由中央计划机关，用行政手段配置资源。其前提是，中央计划机关对全社会的一切经济活动，包括物质资源和人力资源状况、技术可行性、需求结构等，准确地拥有全部信息。然而这是不可能做到的。没有一个全知全能的管理者能够及时掌握分散发生的有关千百万种资源相对稀缺程度的知识。因此，在中央计划机关掌握和处理各种微观事物的情况下，为及时取得保证经济系统畅通运作所必需的全部信息，其成本几乎是无限大的。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">市场经济的情况则完全不同。由市场竞争形成的各种资源的相对价格，是一种全息参数。它们承载了各种资源相对于全社会千百万种其它资源而言稀缺程度的信息。社会个别成员，通过商品的相对价格掌握关键信息，就能够做出正确的决策，因而可以大大降低信息成本。市场经济，是由市场供求关系和价格变动进行调节，即由价值规律对生产进行自发调节。其特点是，通过市场这个</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">无形的手</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，按照经济规律的要求，对生产进行自动调节，达到对资源的优化配置。能够免除计划经济中不可避免出现的资源配置错误，达到较高<B>的效率<SUP>[5]</SUP>。</B></SPAN><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">⑵激励机制。计划经济意味着全社会利益一体化，生产的效益如何，只与全国唯一的大老板有关，而与参与生产的职工个体无关。干与不干、干多干少、干好干坏全都一个样。缺乏激励机制，因而其效率，与市场经济，不可同日而语。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.35pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">3. 市场经济，姓私不姓公。</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">二战以后的世界，是在社会主义、资本主义两大潮流的互相激荡、互相渗透中发展的。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">互相激荡的形式，从</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">扼杀在摇篮里</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">世界革命</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，逐渐演变为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">和平共处、和平竞赛、和平演变</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，再到</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">相互沟通</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN></B><B><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">【</SPAN></SUP></B><B><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">。未来有可能在相互融合的基础上，向更高的社会形态发展。因此，以往资本主义同社会主义，熟优熟劣，谁战胜谁等观念，已经不符合新的世界形势了。再争论姓</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">社</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">姓</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">资</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，淡而无味。命题应当还一种提法：市场经济优越于计划经济。这是确定不移的了。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">市场经济的特征是自由竞争。他的现实前提是多种所有制并存。都是国有，全国只有一个老板，无所谓竞争。在竞争当中，个体之间、企业之间，都必然为了自己的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">私</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，力求胜过对手。当然国家这只有形的手，还要起到宏观调控的作用。但市场经济的主要特征、他的优势，还是在于竞争。因此可以说，市场经济，姓“私”不姓“公”。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT size=3><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">三．国有、集体所有，都不是公有制</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">把国家所有制（包括实际上是地方国有的集体所有制）说成是社会主义的公有制，是我国长期以来的一个最大的理论谬误。于光远在上世纪九十年代曾多次著文辨正：在马克思的著作里，关于未来社会的经济制度的论述，说的都是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">社会所有制</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">公有制</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">社会所有制</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">误译。社会是一个比较宽泛的概念，和国家完全不同。马克思的社会所有制，就是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">联合起来的个人对全部生产力总和的占有</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">；这个</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">联合起来的个人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">的联合体或共同体，就是社会。社会所有制，包含两个具体内容：一是公共占有，一是<B>个人所有<SUP>【</SUP></B></SPAN><B><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">对照国家所有制：⑴企业的生产资料是由国家占有的，并非由劳动者共同占有或联合占有；⑵国有企业的劳动者没有属于个人的生产资料所有权；⑶劳动者既不能参与企业的经营管理，也无权参与剩余价值得分配；⑷他们仍然是出卖劳动力、领取工资的雇佣劳动者。其劳动的性质，不是自由劳动，而是雇佣劳动；⑸按照马克思的公有制模式，企业的民有性决定了它进入市场参与竞争的必然性；而国有经济的垄断性和它同国家权力机构的切割不断的联系，却使它自外于市场经济，阻碍甚至破坏市场经济<B>的发展<SUP>【</SUP></B></SPAN><B><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">总之，国有、集体所有，不是公有制。立足于这种经济制度所讲的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">公</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，不是真</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">公</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">；不是马克思所说<SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\"> </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">真实的共同体</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">而是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">虚假的共同体</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN></B><B><SUP><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">【8】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">马克思设想革命胜利后建立社会主义经济体制的道路分为两步：第一步，把原属于资本家的大公司、大工厂等生产资料收归国有，由政府控制起来；第二步，政府要寻找一定的形式，将社会财富回归社会，回归人民，重新建立个人所有制。后来他已经发现，这种形式就是，实行所有者和经营者分离的现代企业制度</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">——</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">股份制。其结构为：股东大会是公司的权力机构；董事会是公司的执行机构，它直接对股东大会负责；监事会是公司的监督机构。总经理，由董事会聘<B>任或解聘<SUP>【4，9】</SUP>。</B>股份制公司上市以后，任何人都可以购买股票成为股东。在知识经济时代，劳动密集型产业减少，知识密集型产业增加。白领与蓝领之比增加。蓝领之中，复杂劳动日益增加。随着生的发展、收入的增加，本公司的职工，纷纷成为股东。成为名副其实的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">公司的主人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">。他们的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">私</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">，并不需要为了立</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">公</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">而破掉，而是二者密切结合、相得益彰。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>四．世界大同、共产主义，都是乌托邦</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.6pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">大同思想在中国古代就有。<SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">《礼记</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana\">·</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">礼运》的《大同篇》借孔子之口述说∶</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana\">“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hans","title":"“破私立公”辨析——样板戏漫议之七","time":1224086685000}